episodes.title: Dan and Kim Cosby Break Silence on TLC's 'The Cult of the Real Housewife'
episodes.description: Dan Cosby, Mary Cosby's cousin, and his wife Kim discuss TLC's three-part docuseries "The Cult of the Real Housewife," sharing their firsthand accounts of Faith Temple and addressing controversial allegations against the "Real Housewives of Salt Lake City" star.
